:R-HSA-1855215  a           obo:GO_0033271 , owl:NamedIndividual ;
        rdfs:comment        "Inositol phosphates IP3 and IP5 are imported into the cytosol from the endoplasmic reticulum (ER) lumen (Caffrey et al. 1999, Chi et al. 1999, Nalaskowski et al. 2002, Ho et al. 2002, Brehm et al. 2007). The molecular details of these transport processes remain uncertain." ;
        rdfs:label          "IPs transport between ER lumen and cytosol" ;
        dc:contributor      "Reviewed: Wundenberg, Torsten, 2012-11-06" , "Edited: Williams, MG, 2011-10-28" , "Authored: Williams, MG, 2011-10-28" , "GOC:reactome_curators" ;
